programme.title: Ohaa Aramaiti Ep2
programme.desc: Dusun Subpan Segama - Pada masa dahulu suku kaum Dusun Subpan memang telah wujud dan menetap di sepanjang Sungai Segama. Sungai Segama merupakan sungai terpanjang dan terbesar di daerah Lahad Datu yang menjadi sungai terpenting buat suku kaum Dusun Subpan sebagai lubuk mencari rezeki. Salah satu tarian masyarakat Dusun Subpan adalah tarian gabilok. Tarian gabiluk ini biasanya ditarikan semasa majlis-majlis keramaian seperti majlis perkahwinan, perayaan-perayaan seperti Pesta Kaamatan (Runat Kalapadan) dan sambut tetamu. Ikuti misi kali ini bagaimana pembuatan lungun iaitu keranda tradisi bagi masyarakat Dusun Subpan diperbuat..

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Misi Dania Cun Ep4
programme.desc: Dania, seorang Jururawat Desa, menerima tugas dipedalaman selepas dipujuk ayahnya. Di klinik, dia berhadapan dengan cabaran seperti bertentangan dengan bomoh Pak Landak dan menjalin hubungan rapat dengan Dr. Dani, yang menimbulkan cemburu Misi Ilya. Sikap rajin dan kecantikannya membuatkan Dania digelar "Misi Dania Cun" oleh penduduk desa. Episod kali ini Seman cuba mengurat Dania tetapi, tiada layanan pun dari Dania. Akibat cemburu, Dania diserang oleh isteri Seman, Syikin. Qeena balik tanpa selesaikan urusan kerja.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep19
programme.desc: Rian beri Adif 2 bulan untuk berubah demi Farhan. Jika tiada perubahan, Adif harus pulangkan harta, batalkan kes mahkamah, dan Farhan tinggal bersama Rian. Adif terpaksa setuju dan tandatangan perjanjian. Rian gembira dan menghentikan Adif dari memasuki bilik, menyuruhnya tidur di tempat lain. Afeeq minta penjelasan tentang Adif tinggal di rumah Rian. Rian cakap itu keputusan papa. Afeeq tidak suka dan Rian jamin dia tidak akan terpedaya dengan Adif lagi. Afeeq kena pergi ke mahkamah. Rian teringat kes Adif melawan Afeeq dan akan bincang dengan Adif untuk batalkan kes, tetapi Afeeq mahu teruskan. Adif terkejut lihat Adelia berhalusinasi di pejabat. Adif marah Sham, arah Sham hantar Adelia pulang. Rian dan Adif berbual. Rian gembira Adif takkan tinggalkan dia. Rian rasa tak sedap hati tengok kereta putih berhenti seperti memerhati rumahnya.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep20
programme.desc: Adif ajak Rian pergi tempat rahsia. Adif bawa Rian ke pejabat Waris Putra Berhad, JB. Adif kata syarikat ini hak Farhan dan Rian. Adif akan lepaskan semua ini selepas 2 bulan. Adif yakin Rian dan Farhan akan bersama dengannya. Rian ingatkan jangan terlalu pasti. Mak Ngah cakap Sham tak sengaja tampar Adelia. Adif marah Sham. Adelia nangis, tak suka Mak Ngah dan Sham. Afeeq secara tidak sengaja terlanggar Fitrin di luar caf, menjatuhkan barang-barangnya. Dia minta maaf dan tawar diri untuk ganti rugi. Rian hampir dilanggar kereta putih, bila pulang dia dapati Adif tercedera. Selepas bertekak, Adif akhirnya setuju ke klinik. Farhan tak sihat tapi dia gagahkan jugak bersiap nak gi tadika. Farhan pengsan semasa Faisal datang mengambilnya di sekolah.

programme.title: Eidolon Bayangan Dendam
programme.desc: mengisahkan pasangan suami isteri menghabiskan masa bercuti di sebuah rumah inap. Mereka tidak menyedari kediaman itu mempunyai misteri yang tidak terungkap.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep47
programme.desc: Faith menerima panggilan yang tidak diingini daripada Javier, seorang ahli perniagaan yang licik dan seorang pemberi pinjaman yang berjaya mendapatkan banyak harta milik keluarga Aguinaldo. Sementara itu, Love menolak rayuan Carl untuk memberikan perkahwinan mereka satu lagi peluang.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep48
programme.desc: Akhirnya, sangkaan Jose's semakin jelas apabila terlihat Javier di kediaman Elvira. Manakala Karen yang selalu merasakan suaminya Richard menaruh hati kepada Love, mengorak langkah untuk memikat hati Carl.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep49
programme.desc: Jose mendapati dirinya dalam masalah kerana dituduh bersubahat bersama Anton dalam kes rogol tiga wanita. Jumlah wang yang besar diperlukan bagi menyelamatkan Faith dari masalah kewangan yang kritikal.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep50
programme.desc: Elvira mengejutkan semua apabila menjamin keluar Jose. Sementara itu Karen tidak gembira kerana mengetahui yang Carl masih berharap dapat kembali bersama Love.

programme.title: Surga Mana Yang Ku Pilih
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Lintang yang terpaksa menunda pernikahannya dengan Hendra kerana tidak tahu siapa sebernanya ibu kandungnya. Adakah ia Niken atau Hasnah?

programme.title: Huru Hara S14 Ep21
programme.desc: Di hoskan oleh Anas Ridzuan, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episod ini kita santai santai bersama barisan artis yang terdiri daripada Mathni Razak, Siti Hariessa, Cikgu Zack Kirana dan Dolla.

programme.title: Restu Ayah
programme.desc: Ibu bapa Azlan terlibat dengan kemalangan sewaktu pulang dari menghantar Azlan ke sekolah. Akibat kemalangan itu ibu Azlan meninggal dunia dan bapa Azlan buta sebelah mata dan patah kaki. Sejak peristiwa itu Azlan tidak dapat memaafkan bapanya. Azlan menuduh bapanya punca musnahnya kebahagiaan yang beliau kecapi selama ini.

programme.title: The Gear Show S5 Ep20
programme.desc: Rancangan ini akan menampilkan kugiran pita hati yang akan membuat ulasan tentang barang barang yang digunakan untuk kugiran mereka.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep3
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep9
programme.desc: Pada 2015, Adelia mengalami gangguan mental dan ketagihan dadah, menyebabkan ibu bapa Adif berusaha mencari bantuan. Dalam keadaan huru-hara ini, Adif pulang dari KLIA dan mendapati ibu bapanya telah meninggal dalam kemalangan. Kini, Adif menjadi penaung syarikat yang dulunya milik Idris dan memaksa mak mentua dan bapa mentuanya keluar dari rumah banglo mereka dalam masa dua hari. Rian marah dan tidak dapat menerima tindakan Adif. Adif menerangkan bahawa dia telah mengambil alih syarikat Waris Putra. Rian yang kini di wad, dan baru tahu yang dia mengandung, tidak mahu Adif di sisinya dan lebih memerlukan mama dan papanya.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir S1 Ep30
programme.desc: Aidid marah Suzan sebab tak nak mengalah dengan Haryati. Mujurlah dahi Haryati hanya lebam. Zafuan datang KL sebab nak buat proposal bisnes baru dengan Aidid. Tapi dia terjumpa Suzan dan dapat tahu tentang masalah barunya. Kini, Suzan jadi pendiam. Ia menimbulkan kerisauan pada Aidid dan Haryati pula. Hingga suatu hari, Suzan hilang tanpa pesan. Mujurlah Fara di Izmir maklumkan Zafuan yang Suzan dah balik Izmir. Haryati yang kesal, minta Aidid pergi Izmir dan pujuk Suzan balik. Dia janji kali ni dia akan benar-benar lepaskan Aidid dan Suzan hidup sendiri.

programme.desc: Rian berlari ke hospital untuk Farhan. Adif tiba, bergaduh dengan Afeeq tentang haknya. Doktor mengesahkan Farhan menghidap anemia sel sabit, ia mengejutkan mereka semua. programme.title: Deko Bajet S3 Ep04

programme.title: Destinasi Bajet S5 Ep03
programme.desc: Dengan bajet yang minimum untuk penginapan, makan minum dan cenderahati untuk tiga hari dua malam ikuti pengembaraan cara destinasi bajet. Bersama Zetty Nabila, ikuti pemgembaraan ke Sungai Besar.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep1
programme.desc: Din Tiger mengendalikan sindiket scammer yang terbesar bersama Big Boss Mario. Din memutuskan untuk meninggalkan dunia scammer demi memberi tumpuan kepada isterinya, anaknya. Keputusan beraninya membuatkan Big Boss Mario kecewa, tetapi dia tetap menghormati pilihan Din. Namun terdapat udang disebalik batu.

programme.title: Araf 5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang wanita muda yang mendapati dirinya dalam mimpi ngeri yang mengerikan ketika cuba menyara keluarga bekas teman lelakinya yang membunuhnya. Zeynep, seorang wanita muda, kecewa apabila dia mengetahui bahawa bekas teman lelakinya Kadir membunuhnya dengan cara digantung. Mengucapkan takziah kepada keluarga Kadir, Zeynep memutuskan untuk tinggal bersama mereka selama beberapa hari untuk menyara mereka atas desakan ibu Kadir. Bagaimanapun, tiada apa yang dilihat di dalam rumah itu menggambarkan kebenaran. Dalam proses ini, Zeynep mengetahui tentang kematian Kadir daripada entiti yang menghantui rumah itu. Diseret ke dalam pusaran, Zeynep mendapati dirinya di tengah-tengah Api Penyucian, tempat antara dua alam.

programme.title: Ong Bak 2
programme.desc: Berlatarkan Thailand abad ke-15, filem ini berkisarkan Tien, anak kepada seorang bangsawan yang dibunuh. Ditawan dan dijual sebagai hamba, Tien diselamatkan daripada kematian oleh Chernang, ketua Pha Beek Khrut, sekumpulan artis mempertahankan diri yang pakar dalam pelbagai gaya tempur Asia.

programme.title: Wangi
programme.desc: Nor dan suaminya, Khuzairi tinggal di sebuah banglo bersama dua anak mereka. Selepas melahirkan anak kedua, Nor pulang ke rumah dan ibunya datang untuk menjaganya. Dia perasan bahawa pembantu rumahnya, Bella telah hilang. Bella seperti adik kepada Nor dan dia tinggal bersama mereka. Suaminya mengatakan bahawa Bella telah kembali ke Amsterdam untuk berkahwin. Nor mengesyaki dan tidak lama kemudian anak-anaknya mula mempunyai kelakuan luar biasa. Anak pertama mereka suka bercakap dengan dirinya sendiri dan tidur di tempat yang rawak; suaminya menyembunyikan rahsia manakala seorang wanita tua sentiasa memberi amaran kepada Nor. Tanpa disedari oleh Nor, Bella yang hilang mungkin sedang mengintai di sudut gelap banglo itu.

programme.title: Plan B Ep8
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai meminjam pistol Mika bagi melepaskan geramnya dengan menembak ke beberapa sasaran di tepi pantai. Dia tertekan dengan bapanya, supaya mendalami ilmu agama dan mengaji Al Quran. Kemudian Khai menemui Iris meluahkan perasaannya untuk menjadikan Iris sebagai kekasihnya, sebagai satu alternatif bagi meringankan bebanan fikirannya. Iris seorang gadis kehilangan ayahnya ketika masih kecil. Jadi dia mencari tempat untuk menumpang kasih. Justeru, jika sekiranya Khai membenci ayahnya, bererti dia tidak berkesempatan untuk menumpang kasih. Kesimpulannya, dia juga tidak akan menerima Khai sebagai kekasih tetapi hanya sebagai kawan sahaja.

programme.title: Rien Pembunuh Berantai
programme.desc: Rein, seorang lelaki muda dengan masa lalu yang kelam, adalah pelaku kepada mangsa yang dicacatkan yang ditemui di dalam beg pakaian. Dia bekerja di sebuah syarikat swasta dan disenangi ramai orang, tetapi masa lalunya yang kelam membuatkan dia trauma. Dia dibuli oleh kawan-kawannya, ibunya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan lelaki lain, dan gadis yang dia cintai mengkhianati lelaki lain. Suatu hari, Rein dikehendaki polis dan kini menjadi buruan polis.

programme.desc: Kimi dan Tasya ke Terengganu buat kajian tentang Lagu Jong Jong Inai. Berkenalan dengan Daniel yang turut ke Terengganu mencari keluarganya.Semasa buat kajian Jong Jong Inai, diganggu oleh hantu Suzana.

programme.title: Terowong Ep6
programme.desc: Bertajuk ' Surat' ini mengisahkan Ramli yang ingin memiliki harta bapa mentuanya telah membuat perjanjian dalam sekeping surat dengan seorang tua yang dijumpainya di dalam terowong semasa dia berjoging. Setelah dia berjaya,Ramli telah dihantui dengan tuntutan janji orang tua tersebut supaya Ramli membawa darah manusia untuk semahan di dalam terowong itu. Dalam pada itu dengan pertolongan bekas kekasihnya, isteri Ramli telah meminta pertolongan seorang bomoh (orang tua) yang sama untuk mengatasi masalah Ramli yang suka bermain kayu tiga. Malangnya dengan hasutan bomoh tersebut Ramli yang cemburu terhadap isterinya dengan rakan sepejabatnya itu telah membunuh mereka berdua. Bomoh itu juga telah berpesan kepada Ramli supaya membawa korban kepadanya dan dua tahun kemudian, Ramli membawa kekasihnya pula untuk dikorbankan tetapi kali ini Ramli sendiri turut menjadi korban bomoh tersebut

programme.title: Terowong Ep7
programme.desc: Bertajuk ' Mesej Puaka ' ini mengisahkan seorang gadis bernama Dira yang kecewa ditinggalkan kekasihnya mula berkenalan dengan seorang pemuda bernama Aliff melalui SMS. Perhubungan mereka mula intim apabila pada suatu malam Dira dijemput ke rumah Aliff yang terletak di pinggir hutan. Semenjak itu Dira tidak lagi menghiraukan larangan ibunya supaya jangan keluar malam bertemu dengan Aliff. Pada suatu malam Jony (bekas teman lelaki Dira) dan rakan-rakannya yang pergi bertemu Aliff telah mati dibunuh oleh Aliff yang menghisap darah mereka. Tanpa mengetahui identiti Aliff sebenarnya, Dira yang telah dirasuk oleh Aliff sangat teruja dengan lamarannya. Pada suatu malam tanpa menghiraukan larangan kawannya (Watie), Dira yang berpakaian pengantin pergi bertemu dengan Aliff dan Mak Longnya di dalam sebuah terowong untuk melangsungkan perkahwinan mereka. Sebaik sahaja Aliff memeluk Dira, dia terus menghisap darah leher Dira hingga dia pengsan. Apabila Dira sedar,Watie mengajak dia balik tetapi Dira yang telah menjadi pontianak (vampire) seperti Aliff telah ghaib bersama-sama Mak Long ke alam lain.

programme.title: Terowong Ep8
programme.desc: Memaparkan adegan Salina gadis berbadan dua setelah melakukan hubungan haram dengan Kamal. Salina mengajak Kamal berkahwin dengannya Kamal menolak. Kamal memberi alasan beliau tidak mempunyai pekerjaan yang tetap. Di rumah, Salina sering dimarahi oleh kedua-dua ibu bapanya kerana perbuatannya yang telah terlanjur dengan Kamal. Salina mencari jalan keluar dengan meninggalkan rumah kedua ibu bapanya. Salina telah menemui Mak Jah bidan di kampong tersebut yang juga pengamal ilmu hitam untuk sentiasa kelihatan muda. Mak Jah sangat-sangat berharap dapat menjadi bidan kepada Salina. Anak dalam kandungan Salina iaitu bayi sulung boleh digunakannya untuk menjadikan dirinya sentiasa muda. Dengan pujuk rayu Mak Jah, Salina bersetuju mengikuti Mak Jah pulang ke rumahnya. Semasa melahirkan anak tersebut, Salina meniggal dunia dan menjadi hantu di dalam sebuah terowong

programme.title: Terowong Ep9
programme.desc: Ini bertajuk "Cantik" memaparkan adegan Nani menjadi igauan Yusry yang tertidur di pejabat. Jeritan Yusry yang ternampak Nani sebagai hantu memeranjatkan rakan-rakannya yang lain. Nani yang juga mendengar jeritan tersebut memarahi Yusry kerana mengatakan dia sebagai hantu. Sejak dari peristiwa tersebut Yusry mula tergilakan Nani yang kelihatan bertambah cantik. Perkara ini menyebabkan Sidah iri hati. Bagi Nani beliau telah berjaya menjadi cantik dengan menggunakan khidmat bomoh Tok Mok dengan memakaikan beliau susuk. Sidah yang tidak puas hati dengan kecantikan Nani menemui Bomoh Tok Mok. Beliau diberitahu pantang larang bagi orang yang memakai susuk. Nani kena banyak berpantang terutama mesti dengar cakap pendamping yang telah sisyaratkan oleh bomoh Tok Moh. Setelah pantang larang tersebut dilanggar oleh Nani serta dan menyebabkan wajah Nani kembali menjadi hodoh seperti asal.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep6
programme.desc: Haridz dikunjungi seorang lelaki misteri. Ganesh tidak tahu tentang kejadian ini, dia sendiri fikir kes ini sudah habis, namun kemudiannya mayat Pokwe ditemui di kawasan kampung.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

Kham kemudiannya mendapati Vilawandei mati di rumahnya di Bangkok, dan dua anak saudaranya, ahli silat Ping-ping dan Sue-sue, menganggap dia bertanggungjawab. Semasa melarikan diri dari mereka, Kham bertemu rakan lamanya Sarjan Mark, yang memberitahu Kham tentang rancangan pengganas untuk mengganggu rundingan damai Kantana di Bangkok.

programme.title: Congkak
programme.desc: Kisahnya bermula apabila Kazman serta isterinya Sufiah mengambil keputusan bercuti bersama dua anaknya, Lisa dan Ely di sebuah banglo di tepi tasik. Kazman sudah berjanji dengan seorang kawannya untuk membeli banglo tersebut sebagai persinggahan semasa bercuti. Pelbagai peristiwa pelik berlaku sepanjang perjalan mereka termasuk kehilangan telefon bimbitnya. Setibanya mereka di banglo tersebut, peristiwa yang semakin pelik turut terjadi. Sufiah cuba meyakinkan Kazman untuk keluar dari rumah tersebut tetapi tidak diendahkan. Kazman tetap berkeras untuk membeli rumah tersebut kerana sudah berjanji dengan kawannya. Sufiah sentiasa merasakan ada makhluk sedang memerhatikannya. Salah seorang anak mereka, Lisa setiap malam akan turun ke sebuah bilik gelap untuk bermain congkak dengan seseorang yang hanya boleh dilihat olehnya seorang. Sufiah yang tidak boleh bersabar dengan perkara itu telah membuang congkak tersebut ke dalam tasik. Lisa juga sentiasa bermain di tepi belukar di belakang rumah kerana kawannya tinggal di situ sehingga Kazman perasan Lisa bermain menghadap kubur lama. Pada malam keesokannya, Sufiah dikejutkan lagi dengan bunyi congkak tersebut dari bilik yang sama. Apabila Sufiah pergi melihat, dilihatnya seorang tua sedang bemain congkak tersebut. Semakin lama peristiwa yang berlaku semakin pelik dan menyeramkan sehingga pada malam ketiga kedua-dua anaknya telah hilang dan Sufiah didapati tidur di siling bilik. Pak Tua, penduduk paling lama di kampung itu telah pergi ke rumah tersebut untuk menyelamatkan keluarga Kazman dan mencari Ely dan Lisa. Apakah sejarah sebenar banglo tersebut dan dapatkan Sufiah diselamatkan serta berjayakah Ely dan Lisa ditemui semula.

programme.title: XX Ray
programme.desc: Obsesinya terhadap angkasa lepas telah membuatkan Amir untuk mencipta sebuah topi keledar. Topi keledar ini merupakan penemuan baru apabila ia menggunakan kuasa tahi bintang. Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

programme.title: XX Ray 2

Coming from a well-off family that owns a big culinary business, wealthy SK meets Ceci in a gourmet competition held by his family's company. Despite their different backgrounds, Ceci and SK fall for each other. However, SK's dominating mother disapproves of their relationship. To win over her future mother-in-law, Ceci must beat her rival Jade in a gourmet showdown

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Marriage With A Liar
programme.desc: Kiki and her boyfriend of seven years, Sean, are to be married in a week but both cheated on each other three days before the wedding. Faced with each of their perfect partners, Kiki and Sean ignore their responsibilities to each other and choose to go their separate ways

programme.title: Stand Up Story
programme.desc: Mancer knows his father Wah is intellectually challenged since young and has to take care of him after his mother left them. When Mancer discovers and finds solace in stand-up comedy, he learns that hardships provide the best comedic material - from his own school ridicule experience to pandemic woes, misery can fuel laughter!

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: Time Still Turns the Pages
programme.desc: High school teacher Cheng recalls his violent childhood memories when he finds an anonymous suicide note in the classroom. While he has to prevent the tragedy involving a suicidal student from happening, he also has to face a series of family problems with his wife wanting to divorce him and his fathers serious illness.

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: Ride On
programme.desc: Master Luo, a washed-up stuntman, trains his beloved horse Red Hare to be a stunt horse. Due to his debts though, Red Hare may be taken away by the debtors. Master Luo has no choice but to seek help from his estranged daughter, and the incident ends up becoming a golden opportunity for them to reconcile.

programme.title: Crypto Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigation officer Lok sets up a special team to investigate a corruption case involving a banks top executives use of cryptocurrency to manipulate the trading market. When the banks chairman is kidnapped and kidnappers demand ransom in crypto coins, Lok connects the dots and vows to hunt down the mastermind behind both crimes.

programme.title: Princess and 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

Chow Mo Wan encounters many women in his life but is touched by none after he lost his true love. Following an encounter one day, he decides to write a fiction titled 2046 which takes place at Room 2046. Nothing ever changes at Room 2046, and people go there to find their lost memories.

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earths surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: YUM is a detective agency that handles supernatural cases. As YUM investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building, they discover that the spirits are created by a spirit master to haunt the residents so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment. Can the YUM investigators finally find ways to fight against the master?

programme.title: Young Heroes of Chaotic Times
programme.desc: This story is set in Shanghai in the late Qing Dynasty, and talks about a young man, Chen Zhen, who rises to become a national hero after enduring hardships and overcoming challenges in life.

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Polices Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: The Chinese Feast
programme.desc: Sun wants to start a new life as a chef in Canada and struggles to learn cooking skills from a restaurant owner, Au. While Sun will represent his restaurant to participate in a cooking competition, his skill is not good enough, and he has to seek help from a legendary master chef in order to win the ultimate challenge.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Fagara
programme.desc: After her fathers death, a Hong Kong girl discovers she has two hitherto unknown sisters, Branch and Cherry. Through taking up her late fathers hotpot restaurant, she reunites with her sisters by different mothers, and understands her father more from a different perspective, allowing her to finally resolve her long-time hard feelings with him.

programme.title: Golden Chicken 2
programme.desc: The sequel is set in 2046 when a 82-year-old Ah Kam stops a heartbroken young man from taking memory loss pills. To help ease his pain, Ah Kam shares her life stories from 2003, one of Hong Kongs toughest year with SARS, including the different people she comes across and the bittersweet romance between herself and her cousin.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: The Grand Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ma Fei Lung, a Chinese martial arts grandmaster, lost everything after he is floored by a former female boxing champion, Chan Tsang. The relevant video was posted on social media and he became the laughing stock of everyone. To reclaim his reputation, Fei Lung challenges Chan Tsang to a rematch. Who will be the winner?

programme.title: Ip Man 3
programme.desc: When some gangsters led by a ruthless American property developer force a school to sell their land, Ip Man fights to protect it. Subsequently, Ip Man is challenged by another Wing Chun master Zhang Tian Zhi for the Grandmaster title. Ip Man accepts the challenge for the sake of his family and disciples, and wins the duel for the title.

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughters diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Better Days
programme.desc: In this Oscar nominee for Best International Feature Film, Nian faces relentless bullying from her peers as she prepares for her college entrance exam. Fate leads her to streetwise punk Bei, but before they can retreat into their own world, both are embroiled in a murder investigation that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: The Eagle Shooting Heroes
programme.desc: Executive produced by Wong Kar Wai, The Eagle Shooting Heroes is loosely based on Louis Chas classics. Whilst mistaken identity and rampant gender confusion are on the menu, Sammo Hungs action direction and the incredible all-star casts also keep the laughs and thrills coming in this Hong Kong-style crazy comedy.

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: Heads For Sale
programme.desc: Hua is an upright and brave swordswoman who will stand up against villains and do anything for Luo, the man she loves. When Luo is sent to jail by the corrupted police, she sets out to free him and did not hesitate to chop off two bodyguards heads. In the process, she also stumbles across an old enemy of her father who is back seeking revenge.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung and the Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung meets a famous courtesan in Suzhou and in order to spend as much time as possible with her, he builds a direct underground tunnel into the Forbidden City. The emperors sudden appearances through this direct access shock his people but it is also at this time that he helps the needy and cracks the gambling business in Suzhou.

programme.title: Tales of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brothers death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: Lion VS Lion
programme.desc: The traditional lion dance has never looked so good as in Lion VS Lion which captures the most impressive sequences of lion dancing on film. Besides being loaded with enjoyable martial arts chicanery, film historians can revel because it's also the first film that clearly demonstrates the intricacies and differences between the traditional Northern and Southern lion dancing techniques. The Five Venom alumnus and Chang Cheh discovery, Lo Meng, teams up with Liu Chia-liang protege Wang Yu, as they inadvertently turn from vagabond kung-fu school operators into anti-Ching, patriotic fighters.

programme.title: House of Traps
programme.desc: An evil prince has hidden the stolen imperial treasures in a house filled with booby-trapped blades. Amid plasma-spurting attacks, heroes and rogues try to uncover the deadly secrets of the house...

programme.title: Moods Of Love
programme.desc: This Song Dynasty period piece about how far one would go for love (or lust) has two tales. The first involves a devilish magistrate who tries to tempt a Buddhist monk out of his self-professed celibacy by hiring a pretty prostitute. The second is the tragic tale of an exploited young girl who is forced to work in an unscrupulous couples brothel.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: The Proud Twins
programme.desc: Jiang Xiao Yu is separated from his twin brother as a baby after his parents are murdered. He is taken by a couple to Villains Valley and raised to be a villain by a host of outlaws. Jiang leaves the valley to explore the world when he grows up. Will he be able to avenge his parents and meet with his twin brother?

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: Aptly described by its original title of "Money, Sex And Love", this is a gripping drama about Judy, a woman with a rich husband as well as two lovers who happen to be brothers. Jenny Hu is Judy, and her knockout beauty makes this summer sizzle...

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: Ambitious Kung Fu Girl
programme.desc: The lovely Michelle Mei Suet plays a spoiled girl Szu-szu who ignores her true love Yang Fan to go off in search of a swordsman Chin Ko she idolizes. The search sets off one great action scene after another, until she's threatened to be sold into slavery but Yang Fan arrives in the nick of time! This amusing and entertaining variation on the standard kung-fu film is definitely a winner.

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: General Feng occupies the city of Shandong, and soldiers and civilians alike welcome him without knowing his tyrannical and lustful nature. His first official business is to inspect the brothels and take the prostitutes home to become his concubines. Feng is finally killed by his officers, but will the new general rule the city differently?

programme.title: Heroes Two
programme.desc: Shaolin disciple Hung escapes from the burning temple after it is attacked by the Qing army and is badly wounded. He is handed over to the Qing soldiers by Fang as he mistakes Hung for a bandit. When Fang realizes his mistakes, he tries all ways to help Hung escape so that they can team up to fight the Qing army together.

programme.title: Legend Of The Fox
programme.desc: A young man, Chin, believes he is an orphan, until he meets three men and learns from them that his father was a great swordsman who was killed when he was trying to dispel rumors of a wrongdoing and return a lost sword to its rightful owner. Chin seeks out the mens help to take vengeance on the wrongful death of his father.

programme.title: The Imperial Swordsman
programme.desc: Fu is a government officer heading home after being charged with falsifying reports. En route, he encounters & recruits a skilled swordsman as a bodyguard. They then meet a fleeing bride and her maid who asked to join them for protection. When the group reach a ruined temple however, a gang of assassins appear and attack them

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan, Madam White Bone and her sexy sister, and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: The Fastest Sword
programme.desc: Southern Swordsman Ting is named The Fastest Sword but is defeated by a street monk and has to fulfil his promise of working on stone craving with the monk for three years. Ting returns home to lead a peaceful life after that and declines all fight challenges. Even so, he is forced to fight the Northern Swordsman. Who will win finally?

programme.title: West Chamber
programme.desc: The story is based on a famous Chinese opera. A young impoverished scholar, Zhang, is enchanted by Hong, the daughter of an influential family whom he meets in a temple. The young couple faces the threat of separation due to her familys objection, so Hongs maid secretly helps to arrange their rendezvous in the West Chamber!

programme.title: New Tales of the Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone Strikes Again
programme.desc: In this hilarious sequel, Mr Big Potato opens an old-fashioned Chinese clinic, but his traditional methods are rejected by the sceptics of modern Hong Kong. Enter his buddy Mr Funny bone to rescue his business!

programme.title: The House of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: The Happiest Moment
programme.desc: This erotic comedy anthology features three stories about an old man who dies from an overdose of virility pills, a cop who goes on the run after extorting money from a hooker, and a barber's apprentice who encounters a lively corpse in a night vigil. Through playing all these characters, Michael Hui proves himself as a genius of Hong Kong comedy.

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his bride use the deadly weapon - Phoenix Lute to fight against evil, but the lute accidentally falls into the hands of bandits hoping to use it to take control of the province. Gui Wu must now fight to recover the lute and beat the bandits.

programme.title: Melody of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s a-go-go era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: Carry on Doctors and Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: Little Dragon Maiden
programme.desc: With Hong Kong cinema's new wave, high flying, martial arts action of the 1980's, came a new wave of actors; teeny-bopper, canto-pop singer/stars with little or no martial arts background. However, when a film like LITTLE DRAGON MAIDEN intelligently mixes the old with the new, the results are pure golden magic. This costume-action, drama, love story features relative newcomer Leslie Cheung, who falls in love with the Dragon Maiden while learning the art of swordplay. The recipe is complete when veteran kung-fu stars Chen Kuan-tai and Lo Lieh add just enough weapon-wielding spice to make this film really cook. Cheung garnered international recognition in John Woo's A BETTER TOMORROW and Ronny Yu's THE BRIDE WITH WHITE HAIR.

programme.title: Beyond the Great Wall
programme.desc: Wang Zhao Jun refuses to bribe the imperial painter, so he draws an ugly portrait of her, preventing her from being selected by the Emperor until they meet in person. The painter ends up in exile and plots for Wang to marry the Huns warlord as a revenge. The Emperor rejects this, provoking a war which is only averted when Wang sacrifices herself.

programme.title: Lady With A Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman Feng tries to find a group of villains responsible for her eldest sister's death, but is shocked to discover that her fianc, Jin, is one of them. At the same time, Jin's mother and the two other killers are planning to kill Feng. Can Feng fight back and take her revenge?

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: The Lady is the Boss
programme.desc: Wong Hsia Yuan is a traditional kung fu master whose academy is on the brink of closure. Chan Mei Ling arrives from U.S. to revitalize the academy but her way of recruiting students is going beyond questionably legal. Yuan is furious, but when the local triads enter the picture, Yuan and Ling join hands to take back the neighborhood.

programme.title: Boxer Rebellion
programme.desc: The Empress Dowager Cixi believes the Boxers claim that they have developed a kung fu that makes them impervious to weapons, thus declaring war against the alliances of eight foreign nations. The lack of weapons and good leadership in the Ching government allows the Eight Nation Alliances to take down Beijing.

programme.title: The Deadly Duo
programme.desc: The prince of the Sung Dynasty is captured by the Chin invaders and is guarded by top martial arts masters. It is up to two powerful patriots to fight the overwhelming odds and pull off the impossible: to rescue the royal Prince and get out of the Chin stronghold alive.

programme.title: Ocean Parks S1 Ep1

programme.title: Ocean Parks S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Florida Keys National Marine Sanctuary - In the Florida Keys, mangrove swamps serve as nurseries for fish and hunting grounds for endangered waterfowl, seagrass serves as food and shelter for fish and crustaceans, and coral reefs host diverse fish species and endangered sea turtles.

programme.title: Ocean Parks S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Monterey Bay Marine Sanctuary - Journey to a vast underwater rainforest of kelp thats home to hundreds of species of fish, forming the largest marine sanctuary in the U.S. Nearly destroyed by overfishing and pollution, this spectacular ecosystem is once again teeming with life.

programme.title: Ocean Parks S1 Ep4
programme.desc: The Mesoamerican Reef - After decades of overfishing and tourist activity, the second-longest barrier reef in the world is in jeopardy. But ocean advocates have lined the reef with a series of protected areas dedicated to maintaining its feeding and spawning grounds.

programme.title: Ocean Parks S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Bahamas Exuma Cays - Hundreds of tiny islands south of the Bahamian capital of Nassau form a remote wonder that was almost lost to development in the 1950s. But in 1959, the Bahamian government established the first of 31 protected areas to preserve this pristine region.

programme.title: Kalahari: Land of Secret Alliances S1 Ep2

programme.title: Gangs Of Lemur Island S1 Ep2

programme.title: Gangs Of Lemur Island S1 Ep3

programme.title: Gangs Of Lemur Island S1 Ep4

programme.title: Gangs Of Lemur Island S1 Ep5

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep3

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep4
programme.desc: Empty Is The Head - Exhausted from settling his subjects' disputes, King Julien replaces himself with a dummy king so he can play hooky, unwittingly sparking a rebellion.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep5
programme.desc: Return Of The Uncle King - Set on reclaiming his throne, Uncle King Julien convinces Julien to go into Foosa territory. Julien creates a disguise and forces Maurice to join him.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep6
programme.desc: Eat Pray Shove - Clover is forced to take a vacation, and while she's away, she meets the handsome and free-spirited Sage Moondancer.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep7
programme.desc: He Blinded Me With Science - Julien teams up with Timo, the tenrec, a scientist who the King elists to automate everything in the kingdom.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep8
programme.desc: Viva Mort - When Julien embarrasses Maurice, he tries to make up for his transgression, while Mort inadvertently joins an anti-King Julien group.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep9
programme.desc: The Really Really Big Lie - When Julien concocts an elaborate lie, blaming a giant "mega-gecko" for ruining a young lemur's birthday party.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep10
programme.desc: One More Cup - Julien finds a bag of coffee beans in the Cove of Wonders and gets the entire lemur community hooked on caffeine.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep6
programme.desc: Fountains - Puss and Dulcinea embark on an adventure to find the Fountain of Youth to save Puss' old mentor, El Guante Blanco.

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep6
programme.desc: Playground / Sparkless - Cruz decides to turn the sunken ship into a park. But all his and Kelps fun-crastinating puts the project in jeopardy. / Kelp accidentally knocks a boulder into the stream, blocking the flow while trying his unicorn spark. Frustrated by magic, Kelp uses the narwhal way.

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep6
programme.desc: The Ticket Trail / Flying Solo - Lola, Dylan and Cassie have tickets to the carnival, but when Dylan loses his ticket, the Dew Drops set out to find it. / When Phoebe accidentally gets tossed into Nicholas' diaper bag before a trip to the park, Phoebe has to help a baby bird, while Eden and Athena must help Marcus rehearse for his big concert.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep6
programme.desc: Iced Out - Frustrated that she's not fitting in with the team, Aggro goes off on her own with Elbone on a mission to save a dragon egg trapped in ice.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep6
programme.desc: A Ball-For-All - It's Ball-entines Day, the day when the dogs of Pawston show their affection for each other by exchanging balls. But unfortunately, the town is fresh out, so Tag and Scooch set sail for Ball Island. \ If Tag and Scooch want to leave Ball Island with the balls they chose for their family, they must earn them by proving themselves ball-worthy, through a series of challenges from The Fetcher.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep16
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Harmful Horrors of the Harrowing Hiveschool - After injecting all the teachers with bee DNA, the Melvins run the new "hivemind" of the school. But Ms. Ribble is accidently injected with too much "Bee- NA" and becomes the queen bee, overpowering the Melvins' control. George, Harold and the recently re-hired Vice Principal Krupp must work with the Melvins and stop her from turning everyone into her Zombees.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep17
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Preposterous Pulverizing of the Pestering Poopacabra - In hopes of raising their grades so they can go to Lake Summer Camp, George and Harold must teach Ratrick, their assigned rat, a simple task. But Ratrick runs away into the sewers where he is doused with toxic waste and transformed into Poopacabra! It's now up to the boys and Captain Underpants to stop the beast before it takes over Piqua with its stench, and more importantly, ruins the boys' chances to go to Lake Summer Camp.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep18
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Dastardlys Deed of the Devious Diddlysaurus - George and Harold decide to do an extra credit project on dinosaurs to help their chances of getting summer camp-worthy grades. When Melvin brings in a dinosaur frozen in ice, the boys try to get rid of it. But the ice thaws and they meet Diddlysaurus, a prankster raptor who's huge fans of the boys. He offers to help them with their project if he can pull pranks with them, but when the pranks go too far, the boys and Captain Underpants have to deal with the dino.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep1
programme.desc: How to Start a Dragon Academy - Hiccup is given the responsibility to integrate dragons into the village of Berk and must contend with his rowdy friends, unruly dragons and an upset village elder.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep2
programme.desc: Viking For Hire - Now that dragon-killing is no longer necessary, Hiccup tries to find a new job for Gobber the Blacksmith, but the task proves harder than expected.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep3
programme.desc: Animal House - As an approaching storm threatens Berk, Hiccup must work fast to make peace between the food-providing farm animals and the dragons.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep66
programme.desc: Moon Shot - Our teams startup company and their rivals at Baby Corp get in a Space Race, competing to see who can make the cutest kiddie-pretend moon landing for a baby a spectacle sure to bring in a bounty of Baby Love. With both companies pouring their resources into a simulated space take off, tempers and sabotage are running hot, and the scrappy little startup is in danger of getting crushed by their big business competitor.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep67
programme.desc: Inner Children - JJ reluctantly lets Tina take over her assistant duties for the day, but a Tina slip-up leads to an outbreak of town adults drinking diluted special formula that makes them all baby-brained. When JJ discovers this, she works with R & D Baby Simmons and Security Baby Katja to antidote the wobbling Adult Babies before Tina can find out and blame herself.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep68
programme.desc: Poompf! - Crispin Biscuits frames Boss and Tinas startup company for exploding baby Iggys favorite stuffed animal, and Tina is forced to the sidelines to avoid any more bad press. As Crispin expands his plan to burst all the plush toys in the neighborhood, Tina discovers she can stop this by breaking open and rewiring a single toy doll. Unfortunately that doll is Baby Corps current head honcho, Pull-String CEO Baby.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep1
programme.desc: A Cause for The Paws - Po, at the top of his game but lonely, comes across two weasels stealing an earthquake causing gauntlet and tries to stop them, but inadvertently destroys a town. He loses his title as Dragon Master and teams up with Wandering Blade, a knight on a mission from England, to track down the weasels and get his title back.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep2
programme.desc: The Knights Code - Po and Blade's personalities clash as they track Klaus and Veruca and fight off some of Po's old foes. Blade gets to see Po's kung fu mastery, but doesn't agree to team up with him until she realizes that he accidentally holds the key to finding Klaus and Veruca: he has a piece of the WuGao Gauntlet. Meanwhile, Klaus and Veruca continue on their path of destruction while looking for the mysterious "Lotus".

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep3
programme.desc: The Lotus - Po's moral lines are blurred when he and Blade have to break an untrustworthy hedgehog monk (Zhen) out of jail to get more information on what Klaus and Veruca stole from the Lotus. They learn from Zhen that there are in fact three more weapons, and Po recognizes one of them from a comic book.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep70
programme.desc: One Tricked Pony - An overworked and under loved Precious has to choose between the Templeton Family startup business or Crispin Biscuits fun playtime. Meanwhile, the company makes its first purchase: upgraded communicators! R & D Baby Simmons is reluctant to fix the model they have, which picks up signals from her favorite lvorian soap opera, Bridges Aflame. Over a live broadcast, Simmons must convince the cast to tie up every loose plot thread before she has to lose the signal forever.

With Boss Babys cover at stake, its up to the Templeton Family to get Benji out of their hair as he sniffs around for a case that could garner the attention from federal law enforcement.
